Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to this island to \Nexecute a certain mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... It is to capture the \Nlegendary Black Wizard, Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And something else... I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:24.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, um... Why am I on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:09.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As is Fairy Tail tradition, I shall count to \Nthree before rendering judgment upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:15.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The super magic which affects only those \Nwhom the caster views as enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:03:00.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master... Purehito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn those Magic Council bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are so damn annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down?! Do I look like I \Nwanna calm down to you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it be, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You back, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:35.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you have caused quite \Na mess during your last job, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These wannabe wizard thieves were \Ntalking crap about our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings toward the guild are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But violence begets naught \Nbut more violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Caring for one another, in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans were once a single being, \Nand such is true for magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit o' peace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you are still too young \Nto grasp this subject, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey! Stop callin' me boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:23.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master... Purehito...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you form a Dark Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are not both sides of the \Nsame coin, Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is filled with things that \Ncannot be measured as good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:27.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be you good or evil, the spirit \Nof Fairy Tail shall never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy has learned his \Nway with words, he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the "boy".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer a member of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not wish to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you leave now, at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches as well, if only a smidgen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it would be my hand \Nwhich must crush Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you harm the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare defy me, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweep away darkness, rain of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How crude, Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the light, shadow \Nof eternal darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:37.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 28th form of Amaterasu's \Nmagic circle, in an instant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic dances to my will, \Nfreely, without restriction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Defense Magic Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Divine Pillars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaterasu's 100th formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Sounded like an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They think they can go nuts \Nin someone's backyard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them... What \Nin the world are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Let's bust 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you Grimey Warts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Grimoire Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go correcting every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san mentioned Zeref before, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Grimoire Heart be after...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messin' with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana is really in a fighting mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did they break up the exam, \Nthey're trampling on our sacred ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna let them off easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, control your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, there's no end to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one right after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they aren't very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All they have to their advantage is numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, this isn't \Ngoing to end well for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:07.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue fighting like this, we'll run \Nout of magic power, not to mention stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should summon \NTaurus or Sagittarius...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should conserve your magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you chumps wanna pick a fight with Fairy \NTail, bring on someone a little tougher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we to search for Wendy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, what in the world \Nwas that explosion before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia sensed an incredible magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now we must concentrate \Non the enemy in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:38.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Gray-sama is also \Nsurrounded by the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia wants to go to Gray-sama's side soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Lisanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... These guys are dropping \Ndown all over the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna defend this place to \Nthe last, until everyone shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I told you not to order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look into her eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're... turning to stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:33.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That worked well, but that kind of dirty \Ntrick isn't a very Manly way to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wars won't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:50.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can people... Can society continue on living \Nwithout persisting in this endless war?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pulse of battle on the \Nisland, growing stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't it be stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now I was right in \Nhaving high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you supported the \Nguild well for 48 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well, Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have both aged, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:28.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The point of congruence between two \Npeople who walked different paths...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is today the day in which the \Nworld's continuum is completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:40.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a fine master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You led me down the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever has happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic was once born from within darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power was suppressed. It was feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually it became a part of daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the time came when it was \Nconsidered a part of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in my search for the root of \Nmagic, as I came to Zeref, I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That which is the essence of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's story ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It... isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me... my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this disturbance in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I don't even have enough magic \Npower to support my battle form!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy can't recover lost magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to wait for it \Nto recover naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in such a desperate situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you can't heal your own wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave these guys to me and Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this, but we're \Ncounting on you, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me, but we'd just hold \Neveryone back as we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:51.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone sit back and eat a fish, \Ncause this'll be a piece of steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Steak can be pretty tough, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't encourage \Nhim... It'll wear on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super pissed 'cause some guy \Nturned my precious scarf all black!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to punch people more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you takin' it out on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't I turn the \Nrest of you to black ashes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Barret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat that, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:34.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Barret is hot enough to melt stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of Fire Wizard you \Nare, it won't be so easy for you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me... He's the \None I've heard about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayer... Natsu the Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our magic power can't \Ncompete with this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you callin' a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tellin' you to quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zancrow-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't someone you guys can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all, go search for Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle him myself, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As we feared... Grimoire Heart is after...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Zancrow-sama, we'll just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's crazy strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's that Salamander we've \Nheard rumors about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said "strong", didja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a slip of the tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no guild stronger than \NGrimoire Heart in this world, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild is the strongest guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart doesn't need weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... To your own comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear some two-bit, \Nweak litte guild lecture me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames ain't gonna work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about those flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off your high horse, puny dragon hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flames that the Flame \NDragon Slayer can't eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:32.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna eat the flames of a god, \Neven more powerful than a dragon's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames of a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:41.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different than your magic, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking to a God Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... This is really tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've almost cleaned 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Let's take down the rest all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But these guys are probably \Nattacking everyone else, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Against these guys, \Neveryone'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling down from the sky, disappearin'... \NThese guys get around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They cannot beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent will be meh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A goat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A goat... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... He's different than the \Ngrunts we've been fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, suck it up for round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounter enemy during mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:19.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch highest priority to extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense a queer magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell? He's an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:39.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the lonely forest, devils and \Nfairies have a fateful encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:42.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our battle frontier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell? He's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First we have children \Nand cats, and now women?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, stand back. This guy's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight too, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why? Why is no one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov's brats have no chance of \Ndefeating the Seven Kin of Purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are superb wizards I \Nhave nurtured for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:45.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one of them uses a wizardry closest \Nto the true source of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are Lost Magic users!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before this forbidden magic, \Nthey'll be powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour your dragon flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lord Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy can use flames, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:00.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He called himself a God Slayer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean by a god ({\i1}kami{\i0}), anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see 'em a lot in rivers and the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crabs ({\i1}kani{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's the things Lucy uses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are keys ({\i1}kagi{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's summer, it grows a lot on bread-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mold ({\i1}kabi{\i0})!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Fire Dragon vs. Flame God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:19.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:23.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you were actually \Njust joking around with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:25.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
